    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Discretization error GCI < 2% demonstrates numerical accuracy. Output comparison within 12% of experimental data with correct worst-case identification. Remaining 6 factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The credibility evidence, including the primary validation result chain and corroborating literature synthesis, collectively supports acceptance of the CFD model for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for this Class II CPB device.",
